  "title": "Rouding decimal inside of the mustache",
  "body": "I was trying to round some decimal inside of the template. Like,\r\n\r\n```coffee\r\n# application.coffee\r\n# ...\r\nsearch.addWidget instantsearch.widgets.hits(\r\n  container: '#hits'\r\n  templates:\r\n    empty: 'No results'\r\n    item: \"{{{Math.round(A)}}}\") # A is a value of something from Algolia\r\n# ...\r\n```\r\nI checked the documentation, but I didn't find anything.",
